I'm always trying to find time to
practice my dancing with Harghal.

rows.label: tlk45450111_04_msg0003
rows.name:
I try to work hard to keep up
with her, but I don't feel
like I'll ever be as good.

rows.label: tlk45450111_04_msg0004
rows.name:
It's like a dream to be able to do what
I love for a living, so I have to make
sure my skills are up to scratch!
